George Clooney takes the second spot with a net worth of $500 million.In the third spot is

The Expendables star Mel Gibson with a net worth of $425 million.

In the fourth spot is Adam Sandler with a net worth of $420 million. Sandler reportedly earns about $20 million per movie. Tom Hanks occupies the fifth spot with a net worth of $400 million. His movies have grossed over $9 billion globally.

Other actors with a net worth of $400 million include Jack Nicholson, Sylvester Stallone, Arnold Schwarzenegger, and Jackie Chan. In the tenth position, there is Clint Eastwood with a net worth of $375 million.

			
